{"data":[{"name":"1:1","price":"1. அளவற்ற அருளாளனும், நிகரற்ற அன்புடையோனுமாகிய அல்லாஹ்வின் திருப்பெயரால் (ஓதுகிறேன்)","arabic":"بِسۡمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":1,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"bis'mi al-lahi al-raḥmāni al-raḥīmi ","translations":["In (the) name","(of) Allah","the Most Gracious","the Most Merciful","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["bis'mi","al-lahi","al-raḥmāni","al-raḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1409],[3,1409,2502],[4,2502,5840]]}},{"name":"1:2","price":"2. எல்லாப் புகழும் அல்லாஹ்வுக்கே! (அவன்தான்) அகிலத்தார் அனைவரையும் படைத்து வளர்த்து தகுந்த முறையில் பக்குவப்படுத்துபவன்.","arabic":"ٱلۡحَمۡدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":2,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"al-ḥamdu lillahi rabbi al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["All praises and thanks","(be) to Allah","the Lord","of the universe","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["al-ḥamdu","lillahi","rabbi","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1860],[3,1860,2490],[4,2490,5525]]}},{"name":"1:3","price":"3. (அவன்தான்) அளவற்ற அருளாளன், நிகரற்ற அன்புடையவன்,","arabic":"ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":3,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"al-raḥmāni al-raḥīmi ","translations":["The Most Gracious","the Most Merciful","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["al-raḥmāni","al-raḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[3,1240,4565]]}},{"name":"1:4","price":"4. தீர்ப்பு நாளின் அதிபதி(யும் அவனே).","arabic":"مَٰلِكِ يَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":4,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"māliki yawmi al-dīni ","translations":["(The) Master","(of the) Day","(of the) Judgment","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["māliki","yawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1420],[3,1420,4585]]}},{"name":"1:5","price":"5. (அல்லாஹ்வே!) நாங்கள் உன்னையே வணங்குகிறோம்; உன்னிடமே உதவி தேடுகிறோம்.","arabic":"إِيَّاكَ نَعۡبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسۡتَعِينُ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":5,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"iyyāka naʿbudu wa-iyyāka nastaʿīnu ","translations":["You Alone","we worship","and You Alone","we ask for help","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["iyyāka","naʿbudu","wa-iyyāka","nastaʿīnu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,1760],[3,1760,2880],[4,2880,6635]]}},{"name":"1:6","price":"6. நீ எங்களை நேரான வழியில் நடத்துவாயாக!","arabic":"ٱهۡدِنَا ٱلصِّرَٰطَ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":6,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ih'dinā al-ṣirāṭa al-mus'taqīma ","translations":["Guide us","(to) the path","the straight","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["ih'dinā","al-ṣirāṭa","al-mus'taqīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1640],[3,1640,5525]]}},{"name":"1:7","price":"7. (அவ்வழி) எவர்களுக்கு நீ அருள் புரிந்தாயோ அவர்கள் (சென்ற) வழி.(உன்) கோபத்திற்குள்ளானவர்களோ வழிதவறியவர்களோ சென்ற வழியல்ல.","arabic":"صِرَٰطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنۡعَمۡتَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ غَيۡرِ ٱلۡمَغۡضُوبِ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah"],"ayahNumber":7,"juzNumber":1,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ṣirāṭa alladhīna anʿamta ʿalayhim ghayri al-maghḍūbi ʿalayhim walā al-ḍālīna ","translations":["(The) path","(of) those","You have bestowed (Your) Favors","on them","not (of)","those who earned (Your) wrath","on themselves","and not","(of) those who go astray","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["ṣirāṭa","alladhīna","anʿamta","ʿalayhim","ghayri","al-maghḍūbi","ʿalayhim","walā","al-ḍālīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1670],[3,1670,2690],[4,2690,3620],[5,3620,4210],[6,4210,5380],[7,5380,6380],[8,6380,6670],[9,6670,13175]]}}],"chapter":["1 (Al-Fatihah)","Al-Fatihah","Surah Al-Fatihah","Chapter Al-Fatihah","Fatihah","Surah Fatihah","Chapter Fatihah","Al Fatihah","Surah Al Fatihah","Chapter Al Fatihah","Surah 1","Chapter 1","The Opening","الفَاتِحَة"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}